=== Purchase Information === Product Title: LICHEE SU Creamy Lipstick,Matte Finish, Lip Makeup,Modern Creamy Soft Moisturizing Lip Color,Lightweight and Rich Velvet Texture,Nude, Pink, Red,Long-lasting High Impact Lipcolor,0.14 Oz Review Date: 2021/10/29 Store: LICHEE SU Average Rating: 3.9 Product Details: {'Brand': 'LICHEE SU', 'Color': '06#Rose Purple', 'Skin Type': 'Normal', 'Item Form': 'Cream', 'Finish Type': 'Matte', 'Product Dimensions': '0.98 x 0.98 x 3.22 inches; 1.26 Ounces', 'Manufacturer': 'LICHEE SU', 'Country of Origin': 'China'} Review Text: Reviewed by spouse:

This is the prettiest color lipstick for my skin tone. To me, the color is a pink cinnamon. It provides me with a hint of color but not being overpowering and looking like an “over make up” look. It’s a go to every day lip color and a good color if you were going to have some heavy eye make m-up out for an evening. I found it very moisturizing and just a good color to have in my arsenal of lipsticks. Review Title: Very nice lipstick Rating: 5.0 --------------------------------------------------
